_sText:
I made the layout of this map last year and had it dev textured. I found it buried under all my other unfinished maps and decided to get this one done.

The center area is a windtunnel that pushes players up into the air. There are 3 floors. CTs start at the top floor. Ts start at the bottom. Hell breaks loose in the middle.

Spawn camping/killing is prevented by a one-way door that cant be fired through from either side.

I hope you guys have fun with this map. I had fun making it.
